metadata.name: Muchroomz
metadata.description:
Glowmushroom land

This is where your will find the magic of glowmushroom.
As your began the journey, your will find glowmushroom and were amazed by the twinkling glow.

As your travelled further into the cave, your will find by the twinkling glowmushroom from the floor, ceiling and cave walls.

Visitor Centre
The guided tour by the trains that will take you into glowmushroom land, which trains has only 1 round per day at midnight.
